{"tid":2071945,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《東邪西毒》《東成西就》重映　王家衛親自推薦︰失戀睇呢套先","createTime":"2020-06-20T08:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T11:54:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fe32f06851c96d58fbc2979a4d0fddb952158a","tid":2071945,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"時隔27年，兩部分別由導演、監製的《東邪西毒：終極版》和《射鵰英雄傳之東成西就》於台灣重映。在全球仍為防疫而努力的同時，王家衛導演特別拍攝影片隔空向台灣觀眾問好。對於兩部電影同時重映「自己打自己」，他妙答：<br />\n&quot;有朋友問我應該先看哪一部？我的建議是，如果你在談戀愛，我推薦你看《東邪西毒》，這樣可以更加珍惜；如果你剛好失戀，應該去看《東成西就》，一笑可以解千愁。在這個非常時期，只能用這種方式向大家問好，感謝所有的新知舊雨，祝大家觀影愉快，平安圓滿。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200619/350687868550778880.jpeg/nqa6merdplnJmOOOFynftaMz0hXe7XWYBZMZNAWTGTQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200619%2F350687868550778880.jpeg%2Fnqa6merdplnJmOOOFynftaMz0hXe7XWYBZMZNAWTGTQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=419af294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C-J7D_XYqyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC-J7D_XYqyA&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w9XOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=5db28c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C-J7D_XYqyA</a>"},{"pid":"e87a04f9887b1ecd44db6837ccb069e68a50dca3","tid":2071945,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"東邪西毒終極版 唔好睇囉,可唔可以安排舊版呀導演"},{"pid":"c845a222a7d3f144706a308d147fd90e0ce9db57","tid":2071945,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e87a04f9887b1ecd44db6837ccb069e68a50dca3","tid":2071945,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"東邪西毒終極版 唔好睇囉,可唔可以安排舊版呀導演"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"終極版係1080復修, 舊版仲係陳年菲林, 點放上大銀幕?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0effa96d2839cbb7c413a4380168f4315b0bd","tid":2071945,"uid":48479,"l